data.description: Modern, single story home with a country living feel! Expanded, great room floorpan with four bedrooms, three baths, and a large bonus room. Beautiful updates throughout the home that are rarely seen in the area. The kitchen is loaded with storage, stainless appliances, a huge island, and a wet bar. The primary bedroom is huge with a walk in closet and an ultra luxurious bathroom. You'll fall in love with the entertainer's backyard. The pool is stunning and there is endless room for gatherings or whatever else your heart desires! Don't miss this one...
